#10;first trying to use QUIT.&#10;@access public&#10;@return void" ilk="function" line="448" lineend="456" name="Close" signature="void Close()" /><scope attributes="public" doc="Issues a data command and sends the msg_data to the server&#10;finializing the mail transaction. $msg_data is the message&#10;that is to be send with the headers. Each header needs to be&#10;on a single line followed by a &lt;CRLF&gt; with the message headers&#10;and the message body being seperated by and additional &lt;CRLF&gt;.&#10;&#10;Implements rfc 821: DATA &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE INTERMEDIATE: 354&#10;    [data]&#10;    &lt;CRLF&gt;.&lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;    SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;    SMTP CODE FAILURE: 552,554,451,452&#10;SMTP CODE FAILURE: 451,554&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500,501,503,421&#10;@access public&#10;@param string $msg_data&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="482" lineend="605" name="Data" returns="bool" signature="bool Data(string $msg_data)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="482" name="msg_data" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="494" name="code" /><variable line="545" name="lines_out" /><variable attributes="__not_yet_defined__" citdl="string" line="573" name="line_out" /><variable citdl="explode()" line="525" name="lines" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="493" name="rply" /><variable citdl="int" line="542" name="max_line_length" /><variable attributes="__not_yet_defined__" citdl="substr()" line="544" name="line" /><variable citdl="strrpos()" line="551" name="pos" /><variable citdl="boolean" line="537" name="in_headers" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="536" name="field" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Sends the HELO command to the smtp server.&#10;This makes sure that we and the server are in&#10;the same known state.&#10;&#10;Implements from rfc 821: HELO &lt;SP&gt; &lt;domain&gt; &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500, 501, 504, 421&#10;@access public&#10;@param string $host&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="620" lineend="643" name="Hello" returns="bool" signature="bool Hello(string $host = '')"><variable citdl="string" default="''" ilk="argument" line="620" name="host" /></scope><scope attributes="private" doc="Sends a HELO/EHLO command.&#10;@access private&#10;@param string $hello&#10;@param string $host&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="652" lineend="676" name="SendHello" returns="bool" signature="bool SendHello(string $hello, string $host)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="652" name="hello" /><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="652" name="host" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="655" name="rply" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="656" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Starts a mail transaction from the email address specified in&#10;$from. Returns true if successful or false otherwise. If True&#10;the mail transaction is started and then one or more Recipient&#10;commands may be called followed by a Data command.&#10;&#10;Implements rfc 821: MAIL &lt;SP&gt; FROM:&lt;reverse-path&gt; &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 552,451,452&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 500,501,421&#10;@access public&#10;@param string $from&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="693" lineend="723" name="Mail" returns="bool" signature="bool Mail(string $from)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="693" name="from" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="705" name="rply" /><variable line="702" name="useVerp" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="706" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Sends the quit command to the server and then closes the socket&#10;if there is no error or the $close_on_error argument is true.&#10;&#10;Implements from rfc 821: QUIT &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 221&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500&#10;@access public&#10;@param bool $close_on_error&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="737" lineend="776" name="Quit" returns="bool" signature="bool Quit(bool $close_on_error = true)"><variable citdl="bool" default="true" ilk="argument" line="737" name="close_on_error" /><variable citdl="boolean" line="756" name="rval" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="750" name="byemsg" /><variable citdl="array()" line="757" name="e" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="759" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Sends the command RCPT to the SMTP server with the TO: argument of $to.&#10;Returns true if the recipient was accepted false if it was rejected.&#10;&#10;Implements from rfc 821: RCPT &lt;SP&gt; TO:&lt;forward-path&gt; &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250,251&#10;SMTP CODE FAILURE: 550,551,552,553,450,451,452&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500,501,503,421&#10;@access public&#10;@param string $to&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="791" lineend="820" name="Recipient" returns="bool" signature="bool Recipient(string $to)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="791" name="to" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="802" name="rply" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="803" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Sends the RSET command to abort and transaction that is&#10;currently in progress. Returns true if successful false&#10;otherwise.&#10;&#10;Implements rfc 821: RSET &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500,501,504,421&#10;@access public&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="834" lineend="864" name="Reset" returns="bool" signature="bool Reset()"><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="845" name="rply" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="846" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Starts a mail transaction from the email address specified in&#10;$from. Returns true if successful or false otherwise. If True&#10;the mail transaction is started and then one or more Recipient&#10;commands may be called followed by a Data command. This command&#10;will send the message to the users terminal if they are logged&#10;in and send them an email.&#10;&#10;Implements rfc 821: SAML &lt;SP&gt; FROM:&lt;reverse-path&gt; &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 552,451,452&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 500,501,502,421&#10;@access public&#10;@param string $from&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="883" lineend="912" name="SendAndMail" returns="bool" signature="bool SendAndMail(string $from)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="883" name="from" /><variable citdl="this.get_lines()" line="894" name="rply" /><variable citdl="substr()" line="895" name="code" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="This is an optional command for SMTP that this class does not&#10;support. This method is here to make the RFC821 Definition&#10;complete for this class and __may__ be implimented in the future&#10;&#10;Implements from rfc 821: TURN &lt;CRLF&gt;&#10;&#10;SMTP CODE SUCCESS: 250&#10;SMTP CODE FAILURE: 502&#10;SMTP CODE ERROR  : 500, 503&#10;@access public&#10;@return bool" ilk="function" line="927" lineend="934" name="Turn" returns="bool" signature="bool Turn()" /><scope attributes="public" doc="Get the current error&#10;@access public&#10;@return array" ilk="function" line="941" lineend="943" name="getError" returns="array" signature="array getError()" /><scope attributes="private" doc="Read in as many lines as possible&#10;either before eof or socket timeout occurs on the operation.&#10;With SMTP we can tell if we have more lines to read if the&#10;4th character is '-' symbol. If it is a space then we don't&#10;need to read anything else.&#10;@access private&#10;@return string" ilk="function" line="958" lineend="1000" name="get_lines" returns="string" signature="string get_lines()"><variable citdl="string" line="959" name="data" /><variable citdl="stream_get_meta_data()" line="982" name="info" /><variable line="970" name="str" /><variable citdl="int" line="960" name="endtime" /></scope></scope></scope>